<section>
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>A compact settings panel triggered by a gear icon. Uses native <code>&lt;details name="settings"&gt;</code> for exclusive accordion sections with theme selection, accessibility toggles, layout options, and effects controls.</p>

  <p>Runs in parallel with <a href="/docs/elements/web-components/theme-picker/"><code>&lt;theme-picker&gt;</code></a> &mdash; both share state through <code>ThemeManager</code> and localStorage events. Changes in one component are reflected in the other.</p>

  <browser-window
    src="/docs/examples/demos/settings-panel-basic.html"
    url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/settings"
    title="Settings Panel Demo"
    style="min-height: 32rem;"
    shadow>
  </browser-window>

  <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Basic usage (auto-generates gear trigger)">{{ basicCode | escape }}</code-block>
</section>

